!========================================
! Room 30: Mining Tunnel
!========================================
Object room30 "Mining Tunnel"
with
  description "You're at the end of the mine. In the darkness of the tunnel, the silence gives way to a constant dripping from overhead. The tunnel is threatened by dangerous water infiltration and the muddy puddles covering the ground confirm this. The only exit is south, back to the dense network of tunnels.",
  s_to room29,
  before
  [;
    Hint:
