!========================================
! Room 36: Abandoned Pueblo
!========================================
Object room36 "Abandoned Pueblo"
with
  description "You're in the abandoned pueblo. A few bare white buildings are scattered about, their black windows staring at you like empty eye sockets staring out of a skull. The place is silent. There's no sign of the bandits apart from footprints leading in and out of the building to the north and hoofprints heading east. It looks like they stayed here, then moved on, but there's nothing to the east, so they're sure to be back. You can either wait here or head back south along the road.",
  n_to
  [;
    if (rifle notin player)
